markets.title: Delhi Capitals vs Kolkata Knight Riders Winner?
markets.rules_primary: If Kolkata Knight Riders wins the Delhi Capitals vs Kolkata Knight Riders professional IPL Cricket match scheduled for Apr 29, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The following market refers to the Delhi Capitals vs Kolkata Knight Riders professional IPL Cricket match scheduled for Apr 29, 2025. If this match is postponed or delayed, the market will remain open and close after the rescheduled game/series has finished (within two years). If the cancelled match is not played, rescheduled, or declared a tie, the market will resolve to 50/50 for all teams.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire after a winner is declared.
